name: Dullahan (VintageBiscuits)
description:
CONTROLS:

move: WASD arrow keys

jump: Space, O, Up

attack: I, X

as a Dullahan, all you have ever wanted was to find your head, and now it is your time, traverse through 4 different kinds of rooms with randomized enemies and spawn locations and at the end of this adventure...you find your head.

made for the mini jam:98 Empty.
